<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <title>Donate Gifts</title>
    <!-- ** NOTE: CDN Bootstrap.js, Popper.js, and jQuery are moved to the bottom so the page loads faster-->
    <%- include('./templates/header')-%>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/public/css/about.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/public/css/howTo.css" />
  </head>

  <body>
    <%- include('./templates/nav')-%>
    <main id="howTo">
      <div class="container pt-5">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-12 text-center">
            <h1 class="blue-font cool-font">
              How Does It Work For
              <select name="howTo" class="howTo">
                <option value="donors">Donors</option>
                <option value="partners">Partners</option>
              </select>
            </h1>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <section id="donor">
        <div class="container" >
          <h2 class="cool-font blue-font py-5 text-center">How do I send gifts as a donor?</h2>
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-6">
              <h3 class="yellow">Step 1</h3>
              <h3 class="mb-4 quick-font font-300">Choose wish cards to "Donate Gift"</h3>
              <p class="quick-font subtext text-left">
                Each wish card is for a different foster child, created and managed by our certified
                foster agency partner. Browse the wishes and become a Secret Santa to make their
                wish come true.
              </p>
              <p class="quick-font subtext text-left">
                Click the ‘Donate Gift’ button on the card or on their wish page to begin the
                donation process.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center">
              <img src="../public/img/wishcard.svg" alt="" class="img-fluid" />
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="row my-4 py-4">
            <div class="col-md-6 order-md-2 order-sm-1">
              <h3 class="yellow">Step 2</h3>
              <h3 class="mb-4 quick-font font-300">
                Set shipping to the child’s gift registry address
              </h3>
              <p class="quick-font subtext text-left">
                Reserve the donation in the process modal. Follow the new tab link to check out from
                Amazon. While on the shipping page, under ‘Other Addresses’, choose the gift
                registry address.
              </p>
              <p class="quick-font subtext text-left">
                For security & privacy, the registry address is anonymous.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div
              class="col-md-6 order-md-1 order-sm-2 d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center"
            >
              <img src="../public/img/pickaddress.svg" alt="" class="img-fluid" />
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="row my-4 py-4">
            <div class="col-md-6">
              <h3 class="yellow">Step 3</h3>
              <h3 class="mb-4 quick-font font-300">Confirm your donation & get tax exemption</h3>
              <p class="quick-font subtext text-left">
                After checkout, the wish item will be delivered to the child’s gift registry
                address. Return to our site to confirm your donation. Then you will receive a
                tax-exempt receipt in the confirmation email.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center">
              <img src="../public/img/gifts.svg" alt="" class="img-fluid" />
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="row mt-5">
            <div class="col-12 text-center">
              <h2 class="cool-font blue-font mb-5">Ready to make the foster kids happy?</h2>
              <a class="link--blue bdr-2">Start browsing wishes</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </section>

      <section id="partner">
        <div class="container" >
            <h2 class="cool-font blue-font py-5 text-center">How do I create wishes as a partner?</h2>
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-md-6">
                <h3 class="yellow">Step 1</h3>
                <h3 class="mb-4 quick-font font-300">Register as a partner</h3>
                <p class="quick-font subtext text-left">
                    We accept partnerships with state-certified foster care organizations, adoption agencies, licensed domestic foster homes, and other 501(c)(3) non-profit organizations that help homeless youth and children at risk.
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-6 d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center">
                <img src="../public/img/register.svg" alt="" class="img-fluid" />
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row my-4 py-4">
              <div class="col-md-6">
                <h3 class="yellow">Step 2</h3>
                <h3 class="mb-4 quick-font font-300">Become verified</h3>
                <p class="quick-font subtext text-left">
                    Agency verification may take up to 1-2 business days due to our security regulations. You will be notified once your agency account is verified.
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-6">
                <h3 class="yellow">Step 3</h3>
                <h3 class="mb-4 quick-font font-300">Create wish cards</h3>
                <p class="quick-font subtext text-left">
                    Create wish cards by filling out a simple form. Choose wish items from our suggested list, or search & add the product link if the child wishes for a specific item. Your submission will be created as a draft and will be published after our review process. 
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row py-3">
                <div class="col-12 d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center">
                  <iframe width="560" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/P4P6jEqTXs4" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen></iframe>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="row my-4 py-4">
                <div class="col-md-6 order-md-2 order-sm-1">
                  <h3 class="yellow">Step 4</h3>
                  <h3 class="mb-4 quick-font font-300">
                    Get notified
                  </h3>
                  <p class="quick-font subtext text-left">
                    That’s it! You will be notified when your wish cards are published, as well as when gifts are on their way.
                    More questions? Check out the FAQs.
                  </p>
                </div>
                <div
                  class="col-md-6 order-md-1 order-sm-2 d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center"
                >
                  <img src="../public/img/notified.svg" alt="" class="img-fluid" />
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="row my-5 py-5">
                <div class="col-12 text-center">
                  <h2 class="cool-font blue-font mb-5">Ready to become a foster care partner?</h2>
                  <a class="link--blue bdr-2">Register your agency</a>
                </div>
              </div>
          </div>
      </section>

      <section id="faq" class="mb-5">
          <div class="container mb-2 pb-3">
            <h2 class="cool-font mb-5 text-center">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
              <div class="row">
                  <div class="col-12 text-left">
                      <div class="accordion" id="accordionExample">
                          <div class="card" id="accordion--card">
                            <div class="card-header" id="accordion--heading">
                              <h2 class="mb-0">
                                <button class="accordion--button" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseOne" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseOne">
                                  Is my organization required to make a wish card for each and every child or is there a way I can do one big wish card with all of the children that we manage? 
                                </button>
                              </h2>
                            </div>
                        
                            <div id="collapseOne" class="collapse show" aria-labelledby="accordionHeading" data-parent="#accordionExample">
                              <div class="card-body">
                                <p>
                                  Unfortunately, we don't support the bulk creation feature yet.

                                </p>
                              </div>
                            </div>
                          </div>
                          <div class="card" id="accordion--card">
                            <div class="card-header" id="accordion--heading">
                              <h2 class="mb-0">
                                <button class=" accordion--button  collapsed" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseTwo" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseTwo">
                                  Are you charging any fees for the agency partners?
                                </button>
                              </h2>
                            </div>
                            <div id="collapseTwo" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="accordion--heading" data-parent="#accordionExample">
                              <div class="card-body">
                                <p>

                                  No, we do not charge anything.
                                </p>
                              </div>
                            </div>
                          </div>
                          <div class="card" id="accordion--card">
                            <div class="card-header" id="accordion--heading">
                              <h2 class="mb-0">
                                <button class=" accordion--button  collapsed" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseThree" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseThree">
                                  How do I get started? Our agency is interested in becoming a partner.
                                </button>
                              </h2>
                            </div>
                            <div id="collapseThree" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="accordion--heading" data-parent="#accordionExample">
                              <div class="card-body">
                                <p>
                                  The first step that's required of you is to register your agency on our website: https://donate-gifts.com
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                  It will ask you to sign up as a foster care partner and there's a simple form with just 4 fields that need to be filled out for verification.
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                  Once that's done, we will review and verify your agency account & you can start listing the kids' wishes right on our site.
                                </p>
                              </div>
                            </div>
                          </div>
                          <div class="card" id="accordion--card">
                            <div class="card-header" id="accordion--heading">
                              <h2 class="mb-0">
                                <button class=" accordion--button  collapsed" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseFour" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseFour">
                                  Is there a recommended price range for the wish items?
                                </button>
                              </h2>
                            </div>
                            <div id="collapseFour" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="accordion--heading" data-parent="#accordionExample">
                              <div class="card-body">
                                <p>
                                  We limit wish items to be under $30 each to ensure that all kids get a chance to get their gifts donated.  
                                </p>
                              </div>
                            </div>
                          </div>
                          <div class="card" id="accordion--card">
                            <div class="card-header" id="accordion--heading">
                              <h2 class="mb-0">
                                <button class=" accordion--button  collapsed" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseFive" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseFive">
                                  Should let the kids know that if we sign up, they might not receive a gift, correct?
                                </button>
                              </h2>
                            </div>
                            <div id="collapseFive" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="accordion--heading" data-parent="#accordionExample">
                              <div class="card-body">
                                <p>
                                  There is a small chance that some of them might not receive the gift, but we are working very hard to make sure all kids get their wish items by Christmas.  
                                </p>
                              </div>
                            </div>
                          </div>
                          <div class="card" id="accordion--card">
                            <div class="card-header" id="accordion--heading">
                              <h2 class="mb-0">
                                <button class=" accordion--button  collapsed" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseFive" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseFive">
                                  As a partner, do I put their requests in or do the foster students themselves?
                                </button>
                              </h2>
                            </div>
                            <div id="collapseFive" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="accordion--heading" data-parent="#accordionExample">
                              <div class="card-body">
                                <p>
                                  Choosing each wish item may be up to you, or you could gather information from your kids (i.e. what item do they want for Christmas).  
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                  We do offer a pre-selected list of gift items that you can click and choose from.  
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                  However, only you or your agency staff members can post the wishcards on the kids' behalf due to our security policies.   
                                </p>
                              </div>
                            </div>
                          </div>
                        </div>
                  </div>
              </div>
          </div>
      </section>

      <%- include('./templates/footer')-%>
    </div>

    <!-- jquery -->
    <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.5.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script
      src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.1/js/bootstrap.min.js"
      integrity="sha384-XEerZL0cuoUbHE4nZReLT7nx9gQrQreJekYhJD9WNWhH8nEW+0c5qq7aIo2Wl30J"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    ></script>
    <script src="/public/clientJS/about.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
